        "correctAnswer": "interests,criminal",
        "explanation": "Gang culture is defined by shared interests and is frequently linked to criminal activities."
      },
      {
        "instruction": "Complete the statement by filling in the blanks with appropriate terms. Use the Defining Gang Culture Walkthrough as a reference.",
